data.description: 1/11/24 Price Improvement! If you are looking for an almost new (built 2020), very clean, move in ready home, in a private gated community, with a bill lowering, owned solar system, then, welcome home! When you walk in you will love the airy feel given to the space with the natural light, high ceilings and open floorplan. The low maintenance wood look flooring is in all the main and wet areas. The light kitchen has loads of granite counter space for avid bakers and for those who like to entertain. The den is a great place for a private space, home office area, or home school room. The master suite is spacious, with plenty of room for all your furnishings. The walk in closet is HUGE at a staggering 15 x 8. If you like clothes and shoes, this is the home for you. The master bathroom area has a lovely shower only configuration and a dual vanity setup. The secondary bedrooms are tucked away on the other side of the home and are located around the clean second bath. After a long day, the rear screened room is a place to unwind, relax and recharge. Don't miss out. This beautiful home won't last long. Call for a showing today. *** UPDATES, MAINTENANCE and MORE: Huge 24 x 24 screen room added. Energy efficient solar system added (loan will be paid off at closing). Furniture available to purchase by the room. See attachment for details *** Request a showing now.
